+/* Add a list of addresses as bind addresses to local endpoint or
+ * association.
+ *
+ * Basically run through each address specified in the addrs/addrcnt
+ * array/length pair, determine if it is IPv6 or IPv4 and call
+ * sctp_do_bind() on it.
